Java BibTeX API

Packages
bibtex This package contains a driver for the parser that uses much of its functionality and is thus useful both as a demo of the parser and as a template for your own cut-and-paste programming ;-).
bibtex.dom This is an object model for parsed bibtex files.
bibtex.expansions This package contains some add-ons that are useful for processing parsed bibtex further.
bibtex.parser The bibtex parser package - you'll have to pass a (possibly empty) bibtex model (a BibtexFile object) to the parse routine which will then populate it.
